parameters.name: 魔王魂 ダンジョン22

parameters: \F[beni_smile]Akane: "Everyone here is not going crazy. Don't worry."
Mei: "Thank you... I'm saved."

\F[beni_angry2]Akane: "But we have to be prepared... Asama-san will
probably attack us soon."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "Just as planned. Now... it's time for the decisive
battle."

\F[nako_angry]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Do we have a plan for how to fight after luring
her out?"

\F[nako_angry]\FF[syuu_smile]\AA[2]Hiiragi: "Who knows? Maybe it'll be a spur-of-the-moment
showdown? Well, we'll manage somehow♪"
\F[nako_angry]\FF[sumire_angry]\AA[2]Sumire: (If it comes down to it, we'll transform... right?)

Mei: "Please... please save Asama. I want you to stop her
from doing this kind of thing!"

\FF[yuri_angry]Yurika: "You seem to be an old friend of Satsuki-san. Do you
know why she became like this?"

Mei: "The cause... I think it was the gal fuss before. Since
then... Asama has become strange..."
\FF[syuu_smile]Hiiragi: "Oh dear... This is a grave sin... me♪"
\F[kikyou_angry]\FF[syuu_smile]\AA[1]Kikyo: "Yes, really. Reflect on this a lot."

\F[kikyou_angry]\FF[hanasaku_smile]\AA[2]Sakuya: "So she woke up to the same kinks as the
monster...?"

Mei: "Kinks? It's not like that. Asama has always been
shy... She's bad at expressing herself and always wanted to
change."

Mei: "Then that incident happened... and she gained
confidence that she could do the same as everyone else."

Mei: "Even though she shouldn't be able to... After all,
she's never even had a boyfriend."
Mei: "Yet she went to orgies and picked up men in town..."

\FF[yuri_angry]Yurika: "A typical bad girl route. She got carried away
after touching a world she didn't know..."
\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "And that's why she ended up doing such things..."

Mei: "Yes! I'm sure Asama just can't turn back anymore! If
we persuade her, she should return to her former self!"

\F[beni_smile]Akane: "That's why... I want to help her. Ah, I really
understand that feeling."

\FF[yuri_angry]Yurika: "No... As harsh as it may sound... Regardless of her
past, she is invading the school for her own desires."

\FF[yuri_angry]Yurika: "Saving Satsuki-san is less urgent than helping the
other students and teachers. She must take responsibility
for wreaking havoc on the school."
Mei: "But... Asama didn't mean to..."

\FF[yuri_angry]Yurika: "She didn't mean to? If she wanted to get along,
shouldn't she protect the everyday life that everyone
cherishes? Anything less is just selfish."
\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[1]Akane: "...!"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[1]Akane: (That's right... If I intended to protect... I should
have just stayed by her side...)

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[1]Akane: (And yet I became an agent... feeling like I could do
anything...)

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[1]Akane: (Because I can't protect the everyday life doing such
things... that's why I made Nadeshiko worry...)
\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_angry]\AA[1]Akane: (I see... That was it...)
\F[beni_trouble]\FF[nako_trouble]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "...?"
\F[beni_trouble]\FF[nako_trouble]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "Akane... What's wrong?"
亜麻綿咲夜リバース
亜麻綿咲夜リバース

\FF[ama_reverse1]Asama: "I've come to pick you up! Mei~♪ Come on... let's
have a good time together~!!"
\F[yuri_angry]\FF[ama_reverse1]\AA[1]Yurika: "She's here..."
Mei: "Asama! Stop it!!"
\F[beni_angry2]Akane: "Why are you doing such a thing?"
\F[beni_angry2]\FF[ama_reverse1]\AA[2]Asama: "Huh? Because it feels good, obviously?"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[ama_reverse1]\AA[2]Asama: "Don't you get it?! Anytime, anywhere, just stick a
dick in and smoke some weed~♪ There's nothing more fun than
that, you know?!"
\F[beni_trouble]\FF[ama_reverse1]\AA[1]Akane: "Even if it makes Urikawa-san sad?"
\F[beni_trouble]\FF[ama_reverse2]\AA[2]Asama: "!!"

\F[nako_trouble]\FF[ama_reverse2]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "That's right...! Mei, you were worried about
her...!! You wanted her to return to her former self...!!"

\F[nako_trouble]\FF[ama_reverse1]\AA[2]Asama: "Gyahahaha! Return to my former self? To that dull...
useless little bitch I used to be? No way~! Are you
stupid~?!"

Mei: "That's not true! You were, you were wonderful... the
old Asama..."
\FF[ama_reverse1]Asama: "Huh...?"

Mei: "I was always watching you. Those eyes that sparkled
with excitement every time you turned a page in the library.
The Asama who would get so excited when she found an
interesting book..."
\FF[ama_reverse2]Asama: "You were... watching me...?"

Mei: "Yes! Because I admired you! I couldn't do anything...
I was clumsy, bad at sports and studies. So I thought at
least I should try reading books..."

Mei: "That too was forced upon me by my mother. Actually,
I'm not good at reading books either... I was really curious
about you, who seemed to enjoy the library more than anyone
else."

Mei: "I wanted to be like you. I read a lot of books... so
many, so many...!!"

\FF[ama_reverse3]Asama: "What are you talking about...?! That makes no
sense!!"

Mei: "Thanks to Asama, I came to love books! It's not just
because we're childhood friends. Asama, you're my
benefactor!! I found so many interesting books."

Mei: "There are so many books I want to recommend to Asama!
So please... come back! Asama!!"
\FF[ama_reverse3]Asama: "What the hell!! You little--!!"
\F[yuri_smile]\FF[ama_reverse3]Yurika: "I see...!"
\F[yuri_smile]\FF[ama_reverse3]Yurika: "That's how it was! Asama Satsuki!!"

\F[yuri_smile]\FF[ama_reverse3]Yurika: "What you really wanted wasn't to become a bitchy
gal who could sleep with anyone!!"
\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "!?... What does that mean...?"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "It's empathy. Satsuki-san enjoyed reading books
more than anyone else."

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "It was because she could immerse herself deeply
into the stories and characters. Otherwise, it wouldn't be
easy to look so excited and joyful from someone else's
perspective."

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "She was very pure. So when she was attacked by
Reverse Poison and turned into a bitchy gal... Satsuki-san
got deeply engrossed in the new pleasure she experienced for
the first time!"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "By becoming a monster, she gained a sense of unity.
It was like she could become one with the characters in the
books!!"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "!!... So the serious literary girl wanted to become
a bitchy gal?"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[yuri_smile]\AA[2]Yurika: "I didn't realize it! You weren't corrupted!!
Rather... you remained pure all along."

\FF[ama_reverse3]Asama: "Stop spouting nonsense... Don't talk like you
understand me!!"

\F[yuri_smile]\FF[ama_reverse3]\AA[1]Yurika: "Sympathizing is a pleasure! Even if it's a poison
that shares that good feeling!"

\F[yuri_smile]\FF[ama_reverse3]\AA[2]Asama: "Shut up!! Why don't you join us and become the same
as me!!"
\FF[ama_reverse3]Asama: "Uaaaahhh...!!"
歩行紅
歩行紅
\F[sirius_angry2]\FF[ama_reverse3]\AA[1]Akane: "I won't let you...!!"
\F[sirius_angry2]Akane: "Poison Burst...!!"
\FF[ama_reverse2]Asama: "Gahh!! Damn it all..!!"
亜麻綿ハナサク
亜麻綿ハナサク
Mei: "I'm glad... Asama..."

\FF[ama_trouble]Asama: "There's nothing good about this... Now... I'll lose
everything again..."

Mei: "Didn't you listen to what I said? Asama is special. No
matter what anyone else says... to me..."
\FF[ama_trouble]Asama: "Mei..."

\F[sirius_smile]\FF[ama_trouble]\AA[1]Akane: "...I think for Asama-san too... that's true. Even
after becoming a monster, she was desperately searching for
Mei-san."
Mei: "Is, is that true?!?"
\FF[ama_trouble]Asama: "..."

\FF[yuri_smile]Yurika: "It's touching... Such beautiful friendship. To
think that such a noble heart exists within someone drowned
in base desires."

\FF[yuri_smile]Yurika: "I was foolish. Yes... that's what it was all
about..."
\FF[sirius_angry2]Akane: "...Wait, President."

\FF[sirius_angry2]Akane: "Just like with the cotton... do you intend to kidnap
Asama too?"
\FF[nako_trouble]Nadeshiko: "Eh...?"

\FF[sirius_angry2]Akane: "The culprit behind the kidnapping incidents
threatening this academy is... you!"
\F[yuri_smile]\FF[sirius_angry2]Akane: "Student Council President... Onizuka Yurika!!"
